krig ven ikh hob gekumen fun partizan.

472
00:27:06,576 --> 00:27:07,397
OKAY.

473
00:27:11,385 --> 00:27:13,303
dos iz mayne a shvester

474
00:27:13,427 --> 00:27:14,788
iz zi oykhet

475
00:27:14,997 --> 00:27:18,939
ligt tsuzamen dortn avu ale oysgehargete, ligt zi oykhet.

476
00:27:20,953 --> 00:27:22,224
zi iz fun

477
00:27:22,224 --> 00:27:25,419
ts- fir un, nayntsn fir un tsvantsiktn yor

478
00:27:26,050 --> 00:27:27,377
geborn gevorn.

479
00:27:27,687 --> 00:27:28,671
nokhn

480
00:27:28,671 --> 00:27:29,472
krig

481
00:27:29,472 --> 00:27:32,206
iz bay eyner a shikse iz geven ire

482
00:27:32,206 --> 00:27:34,009
PICTURE, hot zi undz opgegebn.

483
00:27:34,555 --> 00:27:36,911
mer fun keynem iz nito bay undz.

484
00:27:45,253 --> 00:27:45,956
UNK

485
00:27:46,300 --> 00:27:49,804
THIS PICTURE hobn mir gemakht do shoyn in Amerike

486
00:27:50,113 --> 00:27:52,115
ven mir ⟨hobn⟩ gekumen tsu forn aher.

487
00:27:52,746 --> 00:27:53,704
a dank

488
00:27:53,704 --> 00:27:55,642
der Amerike velkhe hot undz

489
00:27:56,121 --> 00:27:58,173
tsugenumen, un mir kenen

490
00:27:58,247 --> 00:28:00,063
lebn ⟨avi⟩ ale mentshn.

491
00:28:07,326 --> 00:28:08,622
dos iz

492
00:28:08,622 --> 00:28:10,746
dem tatn's tsveyte vayb

493
00:28:10,988 --> 00:28:12,450
nokhn milkhome.

494
00:28:13,468 --> 00:28:18,524
zi hot mir gekukt UNK nit keyn groyser, gekukt azoy vi an eygenem kind

495
00:28:19,054 --> 00:28:20,651
un ikh hob gelebt

496
00:28:20,809 --> 00:28:22,341
tsuzamen bizkl vanet

497
00:28:22,341 --> 00:28:23,992
ikh hob nit khasene gehat.

498
00:28:24,353 --> 00:28:26,996
oleha sholem, UNK iz shoyn lang geshtorbn.

